United Air Lines introduces the widest choice of services
ever offered nonstop to New York and Washington ...
Red, White and Blue
... First Class, Standard and
Coach ... three choices of service on a single jet.
Choose Red Carpet First Class for the most luxurious
travel ever. Big, wide comfortable seats. Your favorite
beverages... gourmet cuisine served course by course.
All at the regular First Class price. Or choose Standard
service for solid comfort at a close to coach price ...and
this includes your choice of beverage and a delicious
meal on appropriate flights. And there's Coach for low
cost service that's comfortable and complete. For reser-
vations, call United Air Lines or see your Travel Agent.
